{"sections":[{"title":"Going further with more resources","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since you have learned how OUDS works with theme, themeable view, components, tuning and view modifiers, it is time now to discover some online resources."}]}],"kind":"hero","estimatedTimeInMinutes":10,"image":"ic_theme_intro.png","backgroundImage":"ic_theme_intro.png","chapter":"Go further with more ressources"},{"kind":"tasks","tasks":[{"contentSection":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode can use the Swift DocC documentation of OUDS, and this documentation is used to build a static web site."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"But there are also other resources which can be useful for you."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"contentAndMedia","mediaPosition":"trailing"}],"anchor":"More-resources","title":"More resources","stepsSection":[{"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can get it at "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/","isActive":true}]}],"runtimePreview":null,"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-1.png","code":null,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The iOS technical documentation is available online. It has been generated from all the Swift DocC documentation written in the Swift Package."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You will find several catalogs (as many as librairies) with details about everyhting: components, tokens, themes, providers, etc."}]}],"type":"step"},{"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Go to the website and learn things at "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The whole design system is documented and available online. You can find everything about components, tokens, guidelines and principles of OUDS."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"icon finder"}]},{"type":"text","text":" is also available there to get icons for your projects."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"runtimePreview":null,"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-2.png","code":null},{"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Have a look "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" to discover how OUDS works."}]}],"runtimePreview":null,"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-3.png","code":null,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS iOS provides also a wiki attached to its GitHub repository. The wiki is a public base of knowledge with plenty of things: available API, technicala architecture, tips about processes, tests, conventions and toolings."}]}],"type":"step"},{"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To get the source code of this showcase app, go to its dedicated GitHub repository at "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios-design-system-toolbox","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For technical reasons the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository does not embed the source code of the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"design system toolbox"}]},{"type":"text","text":" app. In fact this app and all its snapshots for tests increases a lot the size of the repository."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"runtimePreview":null,"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-4.png","code":null},{"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Do not hesitate to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/